<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/15 How Parents Get In The Way of Career Plans / How To Be A Good Teacher (Host: Josh)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=145&amp;p=149#p149"><![CDATA[
<span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #FF0000">Important Notice: Please refer to the new meeting place at the end of this post.</span></span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session I</span><br />How Parents Get In The Way of Career Plans<br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82aa881dpr0" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82aa881dpr0</a><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Discussions:</span><br />1. How did you choose your career? By your own, by family or other reasons?<br />2. How did or will you guide your children for their career?<br />3. What's the most important for you to choose a job?<br />4. Do you ever think about to switch to a totally different career ?<br />If you already did, share your experience. (or share from your friends)<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session II</span><br />How To Be A Good Teacher<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-FkvBA3U5lg">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-FkvBA3U5lg</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><br />Discussions:</span><br />1. We all have chance to be a teacher. What is your tips?<br />2. Did you have any good or bad experience from your school teacher?<br />3. Do you prefer eastern or western teaching style?<br />4. Does the school district really matter?<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Agenda</span><br />7:00-7:25 Greetings and free talk<br />7:25-7:30 Opening remarks/ Newcomers self-introduction/ Grouping<br />(Session I)<br />7:30 ~ 8:10pm discussion session (40 mins)<br />8:10 ~ 8:25pm summarization (15 mins)<br />8:25 ~ 8:30pm Regrouping<br />(Session II)<br />8:30 ~9:10pm discussion session (40 mins)<br />9:10 ~9:25pm summarization (15 mins)<br />9:25 ~9:30pm Concluding remarks/feedback from newcomers<br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #0000BF">丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第一區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文</span></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=49">josh</a> — Mon Mar 12, 2018 3:41 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
